{"level":50,"time":1776488956146,"pid":997002,"hostname":"interstellar","module":"db.sqlite","err":{"type":"Error","message":"database or disk is full","stack":"SQLiteError: database or disk is full\n    at run (unknown)\n    at #run (bun:sqlite:185:20)\n    at query (/mnt/ext-fast/archon/packages/core/src/db/adapters/sqlite.ts:87:29)\n    at query (/mnt/ext-fast/archon/packages/core/src/db/connection.ts:111:26)\n    at createWorkflowEvent (/mnt/ext-fast/archon/packages/core/src/db/workflow-events.ts:45:16)\n    at <anonymous> (/mnt/ext-fast/archon/packages/core/src/workflows/store-adapter.ts:49:31)\n    at executeNodeInternal (/mnt/ext-fast/archon/packages/workflows/src/dag-executor.ts:961:12)\n    at unknown\n    at async executeDagWorkflow (unknown)\n    at async executeWorkflow (unknown)\n    at async workflowRunCommand (unknown)\n    at async main (unknown)\n    at processTicksAndRejections (native:7:39)","code":"SQLITE_FULL","errno":13,"byteOffset":-1},"sql":"INSERT INTO remote_agent_workflow_events (id, workflow_run_id, event_type, step_index, step_name, data)\n       VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)","params":["1eac9db2-07ba-46d2-bf82-b4d9509faf14","615101356ca6d68ccb8a95eec2aac1e8","tool_called",null,"report","{\"tool_name\":\"Write\",\"tool_input\":{\"file_path\":\"/home/asiri/.archon/workspaces/alexsiri7/reli/artifacts/runs/615101356ca6d68ccb8a95eec2aac1e8/completion-report.md\",\"content\":\"# Completion Report: Issue fix #279\\n\\n**Date**: 2026-04-18T00:00:00Z\\n**Workflow ID**: 615101356ca6d68ccb8a95eec2aac1e8\\n**PR**: unknown (not yet created)\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Summary\\n\\nIssue #279 (\\\"UX: Task checkboxes in sidebar for direct toggle\\\") was investigated, planned, and partially implemented. The root cause was identified: `updateThing` in `store.ts` left deactivated things in the `things` array (mapped in-place with `active: false`), while the sidebar filtered only by `checkin_date == null`, so completed tasks never disappeared. Both code changes have been applied to the worktree, but the workflow halted before validation, screenshot tests, and PR creation. No PR exists yet.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Classification\\n\\n| Field | Value |\\n|-------|-------|\\n| Type | BUG_FIX |\\n| Complexity | LOW |\\n| Confidence | HIGH |\\n\\n---\\n\\n## What Was Done\\n\\n### Investigation/Planning\\n\\nRoot cause confirmed: `updateThing` maps the thing in-place with `active: false` instead of filtering it out. The store invariant is `active_only=true` — any deactivated thing should be removed immediately. Fix targets both the 202 (offline optimistic) branch and the 200 success branch of `updateThing`. Animation `translateY` also increased from `4px` to `20px` for a stronger \\\"sinking\\\" visual cue.\\n\\n### Implementation\\n\\n| File | Action | Description |\\n|------|--------|-------------|\\n| `frontend/src/store.ts` | UPDATE | `updateThing` now filters thing from `things` when `updates.active === false` (both 202 and 200 branches) |\\n| `frontend/src/components/ThingCard.tsx` | UPDATE | `translateY` in completing animation increased from `4px` to `20px` |\\n\\nBoth changes are present in the worktree as uncommitted modifications.\\n\\n### Validation\\n\\n| Check | Result |\\n|-------|--------|\\n| Type check | NOT RUN (disk full, bash unavailable) |\\n| Lint | NOT RUN |\\n| Tests / Screenshots | NOT RUN |\\n\\n### Review & Self-Fix\\n\\n- **Findings**: 0 (review phase not reached)\\n- **Fixed**: 0\\n- **Skipped**: 0\\n- **Blocked**: 0\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Unaddressed Items\\n\\n### Blocked by disk full\\n\\n| Finding | Severity | Reason |\\n|---------|----------|--------|\\n| Type-check validation | HIGH | Disk full — bash commands fail with ENOSPC |\\n| Screenshot test run/update | MEDIUM | Disk full — cannot execute npm commands |\\n| PR creation | HIGH | Disk full — cannot run `gh pr create` |\\n| Git commit | HIGH | Disk full — cannot run git commands |\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Suggested Follow-up Issues\\n\\n*(none)* — the code changes